ply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Alternate Advancement Skills Route</span><hr size=1> I am a 52 Mage, Just got SoL?<br>
